{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/6-move-zeroes/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soobing","author":"[Soobin Bak]","siteUrl":"https://soobing.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"soobing/soobing.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"soobing"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"741d3430-65e6-5244-80f9-4e6a2e172412","excerpt":"자 매일매일 알고리즘을 계쏙해서 실천하고 있습니다.🔥 leetcode의 30Day Challenge 문제를 풀어봅시다.   문제 요약 0을 맨뒤로 옮기기. 단, 공간 복잡도는 O(1)으로 유지하고, operation은 최대로 줄이라고 되어있다. 문제 해결 문제는 해결했는데 공간 복잡도 O(1), 시간 복잡도 O(n^2)으로 해결했다. O(n)으로 해결할 수 있는 방법들이 솔루션에 있었는데 해당 방법들도 다시 검토 해 볼 필요가 있다. 1) two pointer 이용","html":"<p>자 매일매일 알고리즘을 계쏙해서 실천하고 있습니다.🔥 leetcode의 30Day Challenge <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/explore/challenge/card/30-day-leetcoding-challenge/528/week-1/3286/\">문제</a>를 풀어봅시다. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"move-zero\"\n        title=\"move-zero\"\n        src=\"/static/0521c179ae18739e955baab3c1e4c4e1/e5166/move-zero.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0521c179ae18739e955baab3c1e4c4e1/f93b5/move-zero.jpg 300w,\n/static/0521c179ae18739e955baab3c1e4c4e1/b4294/move-zero.jpg 600w,\n/static/0521c179ae18739e955baab3c1e4c4e1/e5166/move-zero.jpg 1200w,\n/static/0521c179ae18739e955baab3c1e4c4e1/3d7b8/move-zero.jpg 1490w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"문제 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 요약</h1>\n<p>0을 맨뒤로 옮기기. 단, 공간 복잡도는 O(1)으로 유지하고, operation은 최대로 줄이라고 되어있다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"문제 해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 해결</h1>\n<p>문제는 해결했는데 공간 복잡도 O(1), 시간 복잡도 O(n^2)으로 해결했다. O(n)으로 해결할 수 있는 방법들이 솔루션에 있었는데 해당 방법들도 다시 검토 해 볼 필요가 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-two-pointer-이용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-two-pointer-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"1 two pointer 이용 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1) two pointer 이용</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * @param {number[]} nums\n * @return {void} Do not return anything, modify nums in-place instead.\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">moveZeroes</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">nums</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> zeroIdx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> nonZeroIdx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n       <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n           <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n               zeroIdx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> j<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n               <span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n           <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n       <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n           <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n               nonZeroIdx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> j<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n               <span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n           <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n       <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>zeroIdx <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> nonZeroIdx <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> zeroIdx <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> nonZeroIdx<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> zero <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>zeroIdx<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>zeroIdx<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>nonZeroIdx<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>nonZeroIdx<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> zero<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"🙆‍♀️Move Zeroes","date":"April 05, 2020","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/0521c179ae18739e955baab3c1e4c4e1/14b42/move-zero.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/6-move-zeroes/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/5-maximum-subarray/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🚇 Maximum Subway","category":"algorithm","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/7-best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock-